name: Kaibyo
description:
This model is an ongoing custom blend that includes a barrage of custom trained and mixed models, couldn't tell you what I used if I wanted. It is primarily used for making portraits of female characters but can do other things like landscapes. Kinda okayish with hands. Works pretty well at lower CFG. Highly recommend using Anythingv3 VAE or kl-f8anime2 VAE

Be warned, this model can be HORNY.

Buy me a coffee if you like my work
Kaibyo is training AI text-to-image
